{"tid":2375963,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"疑涉及生意糾紛 中國男子於柬埔寨被當街槍殺","createTime":"2021-01-22T12:02:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T23:36:10.000Z","uid":56115,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bc7d612704761b5c3a275f9a3b42697b8e968c26","tid":2375963,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T12:02:32.000Z","msg":"一名中國籍男子於柬埔寨街頭被槍殺，大使館得悉後立即聯絡柬埔寨當局，要求嚴肅處理。<br />\n<br />\n據柬埔寨《吳哥時報》報道指，該名遇害男子名叫阿旭，現年37歲。報道指他於柬埔寨西港經營賭場生意，日前早上約了人傾談生意，疑談判過程發生衝突，對方開槍射向遇害男子，但並未打中遇害男子的要害。遇害男子於是立即與他人駕車逃離現場，兇徒窮追不捨，結果在一間賭場的門口將遇害男子擊斃。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，遇害男子的心臟附近的位置中槍，而兇徒得逞後便隨即開車逃離現場，警方現正追緝他歸案。<br />\n<br />\n據「外交部領事事保護中心」官方微博今日表示，中國駐柬埔寨大使館得悉事件後，已經第一時間聯繫柬埔寨政府，並要求柬埔寨警方盡快破案，依法嚴懲兇手。大使館指會積極協助遇害者家屬善後。"},{"pid":"d3ac71bed8a08f37f0235f2569f813b97099687d","tid":2375963,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T12:19:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a1bece4a4eca0e6be8d4926dda5013e478b83f9","tid":2375963,"uid":299514,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T12:23:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed635d3df64e1a1893a13d2e6f23f6d8966999fd","tid":2375963,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T12:33:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4a5fca6a9c3bf206ae69a8dff060f0a479d97f9","tid":2375963,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T12:38:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c600ca006195588aa58554352f90d34763329ac","tid":2375963,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T12:43:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj